{"tid":363202,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"人善被人欺 呢句真係好岩","createTime":"2017-08-17T13:09:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-18T12:22:49.000Z","uid":58333,"like":44,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dfe9daab2eaac2246be59306a62c093960fd6da5","tid":363202,"uid":58333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T13:09:32.000Z","msg":"以前讀書果陣<br />\n份人脾氣好差 成日好躁 好火 有話直說 <br />\n總之絕對唔係nice唔係friendly果type<br />\n身邊既人對我態度好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有禮貌 仲會唔知點解好驚我<br />\n<br />\n而家出左黎做野<br />\n老左 唔知係咪連份人都收左火<br />\n成個人林善左好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好多野都笑笑口帶過算<br />\n身邊人對我既態度勁差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又無禮貌又剩<br />\n以為我好好恰咁<br />\n<br />\n結論: 做人真係唔好太林善 脾氣差返d會好d 就算係無理取鬧都咁話"},{"pid":"4884eb5ff17ac3871b4576fa0f2d89653d3d0a96","tid":363202,"uid":129187,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T13:23:22.000Z","msg":"人賤天不欺 簡單一個道理 怎麼不看透"},{"pid":"8358e2502742146775fd27ba19ac03c84128465e","tid":363202,"uid":104684,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T13:27:42.000Z","msg":"人柒天必欺"},{"pid":"35c86ea789ba72cf9b0f3f06e17fa0c2c6a6f90c","tid":363202,"uid":4173,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T13:28:54.000Z","msg":"出到黎做野個個都係仆街，尤其年過25果啲，真係恰到你盡，待人友善？不了"},{"pid":"36df37f43e3cd7cbea8d82edf4f7ce6558e3fe5c","tid":363202,"uid":76799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T14:03:54.000Z","msg":"十分認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d34ea3d5aaed0283fa294c205b3b5c0aad85d513","tid":363202,"uid":17813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T15:40:24.000Z","msg":"所以有時好人都要放下假"},{"pid":"25b3d6957ffbb59a94c1919714fc5e6a182ed487","tid":363202,"uid":7